# Claude Code Ignore File
#
# This file tells Claude Code which files to exclude from analysis
# Prevents accidental exposure of secrets and sensitive data
#
# Usage: Place this file at project root as .claudeignore
# Or at ~/.claudeignore for global exclusions

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Credentials & Secrets
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

